113 elsewhere, and all residence addresses, if any.
114 (2) The status of the registrant as follows:
115 a. If an individual, his or her nationality.
116 b. If a partnership, the name, residence addresses, and
117 nationality of each partner, as well as a true and complete
118 copy of its articles of copartnership.
119 c. If an association, corporation, organization, or any
120 other combination of individuals or entities, the name,
121 residence addresses, and nationality of each director and
122 officer and of each individual performing the functions of a
123 director or officer, a true and complete copy of its charter,
124 articles of incorporation, association, constitution, and
125 bylaws and amendments thereto; a copy of every other
126 instrument or document and a statement of the terms and
127 conditions of every oral agreement relating to its
128 organization, powers, and purposes, and a statement of its
129 ownership and control.
130 (3) A comprehensive statement of the nature of the
131 registrant's business, including a complete list of
132 registrant's employees.
133 (4) A statement of the nature of the work of each
134 hostile foreign principal for whom the registrant is acting,
135 assuming or purporting to act, or has agreed to act, the
136 character of the business, or other activities of every
137 hostile foreign principal. If a hostile foreign principal is
138 an entity other than a natural person, the statement shall
139 also detail the ownership and control to which the hostile
140 foreign principal is supervised, directed, owned, controlled,
