184 (b) Every agent of a hostile foreign principal who has
185 filed a registration statement required by subsection (a),
186 within 30 days after the expiration of each six-month period
187 succeeding such filing, shall file with the Secretary of State
188 a supplement thereto, under oath, on a form prescribed by the
189 Secretary of State, which shall set forth with respect to the
190 preceding six-month period such facts as the Secretary of
191 State may deem necessary to make the information required
192 under subsection (a) accurate, complete, and current with
193 respect to that period.
194 (c) An agent of a hostile foreign principal shall
195 update the information required by subsection (b) with the
196 Secretary of State every 90 days.
